title: The Adventure Zone: Graduation Ep. 5 “What’s Yours is Mined”
description: The dorm-mates are dispatched on their first mission, squaring off against magma monsters, interplanar behemoths and a child’s word puzzle. You’ll never guess which one of those gives them the hardest time!
author: shows@themcelroy.family (The McElroys)
